        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml School Management System\n\nleft to right direction\nskinparam linetype polyline\n\nactor \&quot;Teacher\&quot; as T\nactor \&quot;Teacher\&quot; as TR\nactor \&quot;Teacher\&quot; as TR2\nactor \&quot;Sectional Head\&quot; as SH\nactor \&quot;Sectional Head\&quot; as SHR\nactor \&quot;Student\&quot; as S\nactor \&quot;Student\&quot; as SR\nactor \&quot;Principal\&quot; as P\nactor \&quot;Principal\&quot; as PR\nactor \&quot;Vice Principal\&quot; as VP\nactor \&quot;Vice Principal\&quot; as VPR\nactor \&quot;Administrator\&quot; as A\nactor \&quot;User\&quot; as U\nactor \&quot;User\&quot; as UR\n\nU &lt;|-- S\nS &lt;|-- T\nT &lt;|-- SH\nSH &lt;|-- VP\nVP &lt;|-- P\nP &lt;|-- A\n\nrectangle \&quot;School Management System\&quot; {\n        A -- (Access User Management Dashboard)\n        (Access User Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Add User) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access User Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Delete User) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access User Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Modify Permissions) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        \n        (Add User) ..&gt; (Update Registration Records) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Delete User) ..&gt; (Update Registration Records) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Modify Permissions) ..&gt; (Update Registration Records) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        A -- (Access System Monitor)\n        (Access System Monitor) &lt;.. (View System Staticstics) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Monitor) &lt;.. (Generate User Engagement Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Monitor) &lt;.. (Generate Performance Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Monitor) &lt;.. (Generate System Utilization Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Monitor) &lt;.. (Generate Content Popularity Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Monitor) &lt;.. (Generate Monthly Attendance Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Monitor) &lt;.. (Encrypt Data) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Monitor) &lt;.. (Regular Data Backups) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        \n        (Generate User Engagement Reports) ..&gt; (Inform Vice Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate Performance Reports) ..&gt; (Inform Vice Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate System Utilization Reports) ..&gt; (Inform Vice Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate Content Popularity Reports) ..&gt; (Inform Vice Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate Monthly Attendance Reports) ..&gt; (Inform Vice Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        A -- (Access System Database)\n        (Access System Database) &lt;.. (Create Tables) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Database) &lt;.. (Remove Tables) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Database) &lt;.. (Update Tables) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access System Database) &lt;.. (Delete Tables) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        P -- (Access Administrative Dashboard)\n        (Access Administrative Dashboard) &lt;.. (View Policies) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Administrative Dashboard) &lt;.. (Create Policies) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Administrative Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Policies) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Administrative Dashboard) &lt;.. (Delete Policies) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Create Policies) ..&gt; (Inform Vice Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Create Policies) ..&gt; (Inform Sectional Heads): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Policies) ..&gt; (Inform Vice Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Delete Policies) ..&gt; (Inform Vice Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Inform Principal) -- PR\n\n        VP -- (Broadcast Announcements)\n        (Broadcast Announcements) ..&gt; (Send Messages as the Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Send Messages as the Principal) ..&gt; (Inform Sectional Heads) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        VP -- (Access Event Management Dashboard)\n        (Access Event Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Create Events) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Event Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Events) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Event Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Delete Events) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Create Events) ..&gt; (Inform Sectional Heads): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Events) ..&gt; (Inform Sectional Heads): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Delete Events) ..&gt; (Inform Sectional Heads): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        VP -- (Access Staff Management Dashboard)\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Schedule Meetings) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Add Staff Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Remove Staff Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Staff Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Schedule Meetings) ..&gt; (Inform Sectional Heads) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Staff Members) ..&gt; (Inform Sectional Heads): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        VP -- (Access Student Management Dashboard)\n        (Access Student Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (view Enrollment Information) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Student Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Generate Enrollment Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Generate Enrollment Reports) ..&gt; (Inform Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        VP -- (Access Financial Management Dashboard)\n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Monitor Student Payments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (View School Budget) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Acce